# Neofetch Test - Auto Height
# Tests neofetch with automatic height calculation
# Height expands to fit all content without scrolling

Output examples/svgs/everyday/neofetch-autoheight.svg

Set Theme github-dark
Set Template macos
Set TypingSpeed 30ms
Set FontSize 16
Set Width 1000

# No Set Height - auto-calculate based on content

Type "neofetch"

Sleep 500ms

Enter

Sleep 2s

Type "Auto-height mode!"

Sleep 1s
